<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
@HI{{@EM{{toki}}}} can be followed by an optional @HI{{ni}}, in which the time at which the relative clause
happened comes under particular focus.
</p>

<p>
A @HI{{@EM{{toki}}}} clause never indicates a condition.
</p>

